<li class='cover' id='bookCover_30236962'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/30236962-the-historian"><img alt="The Historian" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1592232171l/30236962._SY160_.jpg" />
